# UI Component Structure Standards

## Purpose
Define folder and file conventions for platform components and screens in `src/platform`.
This file owns structure and file wiring, not visual token policy.

## Authoritative Structure
```txt
src/platform/
  components/
    <category>/
      <ComponentName>/
        ComponentName.jsx
        ComponentName.android.jsx (optional)
        ComponentName.ios.jsx (optional)
        ComponentName.web.jsx (optional)
        ComponentName.styles.jsx
        ComponentName.android.styles.jsx (optional)
        ComponentName.ios.styles.jsx (optional)
        ComponentName.web.styles.jsx (optional)
        useComponentName.js (optional)
        types.js (optional)
        index.js
  screens/
    <category>/
      <ScreenName>/
        ScreenName.jsx
        ScreenName.android.jsx (optional)
        ScreenName.ios.jsx (optional)
        ScreenName.web.jsx (optional)
        ScreenName.styles.jsx
        ScreenName.android.styles.jsx (optional)
        ScreenName.ios.styles.jsx (optional)
        ScreenName.web.styles.jsx (optional)
        useScreenName.js (optional)
        types.js (optional)
        index.js
```

## Grouping Rules
- Components/screens must be inside category folders.
- Parentheses folders are not used in `src/platform`.
- Root-level `components/<Name>/` and `screens/<Name>/` are forbidden.

## Shared-First Platform Strategy
- Start with unsuffixed shared files.
- Add platform files only when behavior or markup differs.
- Keep props/API equivalent across shared and override implementations.

## Style Wiring Rules
- Each platform implementation imports matching style file (or shared style file when no override exists).
- Do not import one platform override style file from another platform override style file.
- Style policy details (tokens, styled-components, `StyleSheet` exceptions) are owned by `theme-design.mdc`.

## Logic Placement
- Rendering in component/screen files.
- Reusable view logic in local `use*.js` hooks.
- Local contracts/constants in `types.js`.

## Export & Import Rules
- Local barrel is always `index.js` (exports only).
- Avoid ancestor barrel imports from files re-exported by those barrels.
- Internal component-to-component imports must target leaf component barrels.
- Do not import `@platform/components` from within `src/platform/components/**`.

## Naming
- Components/screens/layouts: `PascalCase`
- Hooks: `use` + `PascalCase`
- Style files: `[Name].styles.jsx` and `[Name].<platform>.styles.jsx`
- Local contracts: `types.js`

## Related Owners
- Runtime UI behavior: `platform-ui.mdc`
- Styling and tokens: `theme-design.mdc`
- Global naming/export conventions: `coding-conventions.mdc`
